      "description": "This 2017 Porsche Macan S is the perfect blend of performance and utility, presented in a striking Volcano Grey Metallic that still holds a deep, mirror-like shine. As a meticulous owner, I\u2019ve ensured this vehicle has been garage-kept and professionally detailed regularly. The exterior is in wonderful shape, save for a few minor stone chips on the front fascia consistent with standard highway use. Inside, the Agate Grey leather interior remains plush and supportive; the seats show only very light softening on the driver\u2019s side bolster, and the cabin is strictly smoke-free. Every electronic feature, from the panoramic sunroof to the premium Bose surround sound system and navigation, functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, this Macan is exceptionally solid. It comes with a complete, documented service history from authorized dealerships, including a recent major service and a fresh set of Michelin Latitude Sport 3 tires. The 3.0L V6 biturbo engine delivers power smoothly through the 7-speed PDK transmission, providing a driving experience that is both spirited and reliable. This is a turn-key vehicle ready for its next owner to enjoy immediately.",
